<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Keynotfound on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/keynotfound/</link><description>Recent content in Keynotfound on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/keynotfound/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Swift Error — Key Not Found in Dictionary</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/dictionary-key/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/dictionary-key/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="key-not-found-in-dictionary"&gt;Key Not Found in Dictionary&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you force-unwrap a dictionary subscript for a key that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist, or when iterating over keys that have been removed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dictionaries in Swift return optionals when accessed by subscript. If you force-unwrap (&lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt;) the result and the key doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist, the runtime crashes. This is common with misspelled keys, keys from external data, or assumptions about dictionary contents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common patterns:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Swift KeyNotFoundError Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/keynotfounderror-swift/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/keynotfounderror-swift/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;KeyNotFoundError&lt;/code&gt; occurs when you access a dictionary with a key that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist and no default value is provided. In Swift, dictionary subscript returns an optional, but force-unwrapping nil causes a crash.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accessing non-existent key with force unwrap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typo in key name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data structure changed but code wasn&amp;rsquo;t updated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing initialization of dictionary values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Force unwrapping non-existent key&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; age = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;age&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Use optional binding&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; age = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;age&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(age)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Key not found&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Not providing default value&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; scores = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;math&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;95&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; science = scores[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;science&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Provide default value&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; science = scores[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;science&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] ?? &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Typo in key&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; config = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;host&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;localhost&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; port = config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;prot&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// nil (typo)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Verify key exists&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; port = config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;port&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] ?? &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;3000&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe dictionary access&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;c&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(value) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Default values&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; defaults = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;color&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;blue&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;size&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;medium&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; font = defaults[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;font&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] ?? &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Arial&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 3: Dictionary with default&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; counts: [String: Int] = [:]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;counts[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;apple&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;counts[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;apple&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;print(counts[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;apple&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="index-out-of-range-swift"&gt;Index out of range&lt;/a&gt; — array index beyond bounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="nil-unwrap-error"&gt;Nil unwrap error&lt;/a&gt; — force unwrapping nil&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="decoding-error-swift"&gt;Decoding error&lt;/a&gt; — JSON decoding failed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>KeyNotFoundException in F#</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-notfoundexception/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/fsharp/fsharp-notfoundexception/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;KeyNotFoundException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when accessing a key in a dictionary or map that does not exist. This is thrown by the indexer &lt;code&gt;dict.[key]&lt;/code&gt; when the key is missing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accessing non-existent key with indexer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typo in key name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Key not added to dictionary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Case sensitivity mismatch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;TryGetValue&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fsharp" data-lang="fsharp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;open&lt;/span&gt; System.Collections.Generic
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Dictionary&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; int&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;dict&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;Add&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;one&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; 1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;match&lt;/span&gt; dict&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;TryGetValue&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;two&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;with&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; value &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; printfn &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Found: %d&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; value
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; printfn &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Key not found&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;Map.tryFind&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>